65 void AckermannEkf::bring_time_forward_to(double time) {
66  if (time > this->time) {
67  // Only predict if the filter time has been initialized, otherwise dt
68  // may be VERY large
69  if (this->time >= 0) {
70  predict(time - this->time);
71  }
72  this->time = time;
73  }
74 }

76 void AckermannEkf::predict(double dt) {
77  if (control_signal_enabled_) {
78  // Accelration is linear gain on velocity error
79  x(State::accel) = boost::algorithm::clamp(
80  (control_signal_.u(ControlSignal::speed) - x(State::speed)) *
81  control_acceleration_gain_,
82  -max_control_acceleration_, max_control_acceleration_);
83 
84  double steering_angle = atan(wheelbase_ * x(State::dyaw_dx));
85  // Add (steering angle speed) * dt to steering angle, where steering
86  // angle speed is linear gain on steering angle error
87  steering_angle +=
88  boost::algorithm::clamp(
89  (control_signal_.u(ControlSignal::angle) - steering_angle) *
90  control_angle_speed_gain_,
91  -max_control_angle_speed_, max_control_angle_speed_) *
92  dt;
93  steering_angle = boost::algorithm::clamp(steering_angle, -M_PI * 0.499,
94  M_PI * 0.499);
95 
96  x(State::dyaw_dx) = tan(steering_angle) / wheelbase_;
97 
98  constrain_state();
99  }

212  H(Measurement::Y, State::Yaw) = -measurement.sensor_position(1)*(cos(x(State::Roll))*sin(x(State::Yaw))-cos(x(State::Yaw))*sin(x(State::Pitch))*sin(x(State::Roll)))+measurement.sensor_position(2)*(sin(x(State::Roll))*sin(x(State::Yaw))+cos(x(State::Roll))*cos(x(State::Yaw))*sin(x(State::Pitch)))+measurement.sensor_position(0)*cos(x(State::Pitch))*cos(x(State::Yaw));
213  H(Measurement::Z, State::Z) = 1.0;
214  H(Measurement::Z, State::Roll) = cos(x(State::Pitch))*(measurement.sensor_position(1)*cos(x(State::Roll))-measurement.sensor_position(2)*sin(x(State::Roll)));
215  H(Measurement::Z, State::Pitch) = -measurement.sensor_position(0)*cos(x(State::Pitch))-measurement.sensor_position(2)*cos(x(State::Roll))*sin(x(State::Pitch))-measurement.sensor_position(1)*sin(x(State::Pitch))*sin(x(State::Roll));
216  H(Measurement::dx_dt, State::speed) = x(State::dpitch_dx)*measurement.sensor_position(2)-x(State::dyaw_dx)*measurement.sensor_position(1)+1.0;
217  H(Measurement::dx_dt, State::dpitch_dx) = measurement.sensor_position(2)*x(State::speed);
218  H(Measurement::dx_dt, State::dyaw_dx) = -measurement.sensor_position(1)*x(State::speed);
219  H(Measurement::dy_dt, State::speed) = -x(State::droll_dx)*measurement.sensor_position(2)+x(State::dyaw_dx)*measurement.sensor_position(0);
220  H(Measurement::dy_dt, State::droll_dx) = -measurement.sensor_position(2)*x(State::speed);
221  H(Measurement::dy_dt, State::dyaw_dx) = measurement.sensor_position(0)*x(State::speed);
222  H(Measurement::dz_dt, State::speed) = -x(State::dpitch_dx)*measurement.sensor_position(0)+x(State::droll_dx)*measurement.sensor_position(1);
223  H(Measurement::dz_dt, State::droll_dx) = measurement.sensor_position(1)*x(State::speed);
224  H(Measurement::dz_dt, State::dpitch_dx) = -measurement.sensor_position(0)*x(State::speed);
225  H(Measurement::d2x_dt2, State::speed) = x(State::speed)*((x(State::dpitch_dx)*x(State::dpitch_dx))*measurement.sensor_position(0)+(x(State::dyaw_dx)*x(State::dyaw_dx))*measurement.sensor_position(0)-x(State::dpitch_dx)*x(State::droll_dx)*measurement.sensor_position(1)-x(State::droll_dx)*x(State::dyaw_dx)*measurement.sensor_position(2))*-2.0;
226  H(Measurement::d2x_dt2, State::accel) = x(State::dpitch_dx)*measurement.sensor_position(2)-x(State::dyaw_dx)*measurement.sensor_position(1)+1.0;
227  H(Measurement::d2x_dt2, State::Pitch) = -measurement.gravity*cos(x(State::Pitch));
228  H(Measurement::d2x_dt2, State::droll_dx) = (x(State::speed)*x(State::speed))*(x(State::dpitch_dx)*measurement.sensor_position(1)+x(State::dyaw_dx)*measurement.sensor_position(2));
229  H(Measurement::d2x_dt2, State::dpitch_dx) = x(State::accel)*measurement.sensor_position(2)-x(State::dpitch_dx)*measurement.sensor_position(0)*(x(State::speed)*x(State::speed))*2.0+x(State::droll_dx)*measurement.sensor_position(1)*(x(State::speed)*x(State::speed));
230  H(Measurement::d2x_dt2, State::dyaw_dx) = -x(State::accel)*measurement.sensor_position(1)+x(State::droll_dx)*measurement.sensor_position(2)*(x(State::speed)*x(State::speed))-x(State::dyaw_dx)*measurement.sensor_position(0)*(x(State::speed)*x(State::speed))*2.0;
231  H(Measurement::d2y_dt2, State::speed) = x(State::speed)*(x(State::dyaw_dx)-(x(State::droll_dx)*x(State::droll_dx))*measurement.sensor_position(1)-(x(State::dyaw_dx)*x(State::dyaw_dx))*measurement.sensor_position(1)+x(State::dpitch_dx)*x(State::droll_dx)*measurement.sensor_position(0)+x(State::dpitch_dx)*x(State::dyaw_dx)*measurement.sensor_position(2))*2.0;
232  H(Measurement::d2y_dt2, State::accel) = -x(State::droll_dx)*measurement.sensor_position(2)+x(State::dyaw_dx)*measurement.sensor_position(0);
233  H(Measurement::d2y_dt2, State::Roll) = measurement.gravity*cos(x(State::Pitch))*cos(x(State::Roll));
234  H(Measurement::d2y_dt2, State::Pitch) = -measurement.gravity*sin(x(State::Pitch))*sin(x(State::Roll));
235  H(Measurement::d2y_dt2, State::droll_dx) = -x(State::accel)*measurement.sensor_position(2)+x(State::dpitch_dx)*measurement.sensor_position(0)*(x(State::speed)*x(State::speed))-x(State::droll_dx)*measurement.sensor_position(1)*(x(State::speed)*x(State::speed))*2.0;
236  H(Measurement::d2y_dt2, State::dpitch_dx) = (x(State::speed)*x(State::speed))*(x(State::droll_dx)*measurement.sensor_position(0)+x(State::dyaw_dx)*measurement.sensor_position(2));
237  H(Measurement::d2y_dt2, State::dyaw_dx) = x(State::accel)*measurement.sensor_position(0)+x(State::speed)*x(State::speed)+x(State::dpitch_dx)*measurement.sensor_position(2)*(x(State::speed)*x(State::speed))-x(State::dyaw_dx)*measurement.sensor_position(1)*(x(State::speed)*x(State::speed))*2.0;
238  H(Measurement::d2z_dt2, State::speed) = x(State::speed)*(x(State::dpitch_dx)+(x(State::dpitch_dx)*x(State::dpitch_dx))*measurement.sensor_position(2)+(x(State::droll_dx)*x(State::droll_dx))*measurement.sensor_position(2)-x(State::dpitch_dx)*x(State::dyaw_dx)*measurement.sensor_position(1)-x(State::droll_dx)*x(State::dyaw_dx)*measurement.sensor_position(0))*-2.0;
239  H(Measurement::d2z_dt2, State::accel) = -x(State::dpitch_dx)*measurement.sensor_position(0)+x(State::droll_dx)*measurement.sensor_position(1);
240  H(Measurement::d2z_dt2, State::Roll) = -measurement.gravity*cos(x(State::Pitch))*sin(x(State::Roll));
241  H(Measurement::d2z_dt2, State::Pitch) = -measurement.gravity*cos(x(State::Roll))*sin(x(State::Pitch));
242  H(Measurement::d2z_dt2, State::droll_dx) = x(State::accel)*measurement.sensor_position(1)-x(State::droll_dx)*measurement.sensor_position(2)*(x(State::speed)*x(State::speed))*2.0+x(State::dyaw_dx)*measurement.sensor_position(0)*(x(State::speed)*x(State::speed));
243  H(Measurement::d2z_dt2, State::dpitch_dx) = -x(State::accel)*measurement.sensor_position(0)-x(State::speed)*x(State::speed)-x(State::dpitch_dx)*measurement.sensor_position(2)*(x(State::speed)*x(State::speed))*2.0+x(State::dyaw_dx)*measurement.sensor_position(1)*(x(State::speed)*x(State::speed));
244  H(Measurement::d2z_dt2, State::dyaw_dx) = (x(State::speed)*x(State::speed))*(x(State::dpitch_dx)*measurement.sensor_position(1)+x(State::droll_dx)*measurement.sensor_position(0));
245  H(Measurement::Roll, State::Roll) = 1.0;
246  H(Measurement::Pitch, State::Pitch) = 1.0;
247  H(Measurement::Yaw, State::Yaw) = 1.0;
248  H(Measurement::droll_dt, State::speed) = x(State::droll_dx);
249  H(Measurement::droll_dt, State::droll_dx) = x(State::speed);
250  H(Measurement::dpitch_dt, State::speed) = x(State::dpitch_dx);
251  H(Measurement::dpitch_dt, State::dpitch_dx) = x(State::speed);
252  H(Measurement::dyaw_dt, State::speed) = x(State::dyaw_dx);
253  H(Measurement::dyaw_dt, State::dyaw_dx) = x(State::speed);
254 
255  // clang-format on
256 
257  // Find the indicies of values to include in correction step
258  std::vector<int> measurement_indices;
259  for (int i = 0; i < MEASUREMENT_SIZE; i++) {
260  if (measurement.mask[i]) {
261  measurement_indices.push_back(i);
262  }
263  }
264 
265  // Create subsets of z, R, h and H from the indicies of given by the
266  // measurement mask. There is no need to work with e.g. the full h vector
267  // if only two out of MEASUREMENT_SIZE components are actually used
268  // By creating this subset we e.g. in this example only have to invert a 2x2
269  // matrix as opposed to a MEASUREMENT_SIZExMEASUREMENT_SIZE one
270  Eigen::MatrixXd R(measurement_indices.size(), measurement_indices.size());
271  Eigen::VectorXd y(measurement_indices.size());
272  Eigen::MatrixXd H_subset(measurement_indices.size(), STATE_SIZE);
273  for (int i_ = 0; i_ < measurement_indices.size(); i_++) {
274  int i = measurement_indices[i_];
275 
276  // Subset h and z (and y)
277  y(i_) = measurement.z(i) - h(i);
278 
279  // Wrap Yaw error (a == 2*pi*n + a)
280  if (i_ == Measurement::Yaw) {
281  y(i_) -= round(y(i_) / (2 * M_PI)) * 2 * M_PI;
282  }
283 
284  // Subset R
285  for (int j_ = 0; j_ < measurement_indices.size(); j_++) {
286  int j = measurement_indices[j_];
287 
288  R(i_, j_) = measurement.R(i, j);
289  }
290 
291  // Subset H
292  for (int j = 0; j < STATE_SIZE; j++) { H_subset(i_, j) = H(i, j); }
293  }
294 
295  // Kalman correction equations according to wikipeadia on EKF
296  Eigen::MatrixXd K = P * H_subset.transpose() *
297  (H_subset * P * H_subset.transpose() + R).inverse();
298  x.noalias() += K * y;
299  constrain_state();
300  P = (Eigen::MatrixXd::Identity(STATE_SIZE, STATE_SIZE) - K * H_subset) * P;
301 }
302 
303 void AckermannEkf::constrain_state() {
304  x.noalias() = x.cwiseMax(x_min_).cwiseMin(x_max_);
305 }
